pplications that provide real-time forecasts, location-based updates, temperature details, and intuitive user interfaces for accurate and easy weather monitoring.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></section>\n<!-- /wp:group --></main>\n<!-- /wp:group -->', 'Front Page', 'Displays your site\'s homepage, whether it is set to display latest posts or a static page. The Front Page template takes precedence over all templates.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '8-revision-v1', '', '', '2026-04-02 10:30:46', '2026-04-02 10:30:46', '', 8, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=73', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
